house_listing.house_description: Great home in Round Rock. Seconds from Dell. Wood floors in entrance leading to tile floors in kitchen and breakfast area. Custom tile backsplash in kitchen. Master suite with walk-in closet. Other features: 2 inch wood blinds, inside utility room, ceiling fans, garage door opener, security system, and fenced yard with landscaping.
